casebody.data:
Darrell BENJAMIN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4838 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 2, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

As the judgment and sentence sought to be appealed in the petition for belated appeal is the subject of review in appeal number 2D17-4818, the petition is dismissed, and the case shall proceed under case number 2D17-4818.

LaROSE, C.J., and CASANUEVA and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
